data.description: Large 4 bedroom home with great views of the Mogollon Rim. Fenced back yard with storage shed and fire pit.  Upgraded master bathroom. Plenty of room to park R.V. and other toys. Easy walk to the Tonto National Forest. Great family home or possible VRBO. Interior of home freshly painted, brand new carpet. Price per square foot makes this home one of the best buys on the market.
